// Look — an Axis2D action. Only mouse X (yaw) is bound, in the context;
// the y/pitch axis would require a Swizzle modifier, which the engine's
// on-disk modifier encoding can't round-trip, so the follow camera
// orbits in yaw only. The CameraRig's `look_action` reads this.
(
    name: "Look",
    value_kind: Axis2D,
)
